to eat or drink or do something.

462
00:46:53,724 --> 00:46:56,762
What about the important thing
I wanted to tell you about?

463
00:46:56,764 --> 00:47:00,385
"Well, I got something to tell you too."
- Shoot!

464
00:47:02,757 --> 00:47:06,045
In everyone's presence?
"- That's right, come on."

465
00:47:06,753 --> 00:47:10,250
Where are you taking him? He just
arrived. Let him change and eat...

466
00:47:10,666 --> 00:47:13,704
"No, this is an emergency."
Come on.

467
00:47:13,704 --> 00:47:15,744
My uniform tie!
- Sit there.

468
00:47:15,744 --> 00:47:18,239
My badge...

469
00:47:18,242 --> 00:47:20,405
"Now tell me, what have you to say?"
- Your turn first.

470
00:47:20,407 --> 00:47:22,570
"No, you go first."
- No you.

471
00:47:22,572 --> 00:47:25,693
I think we both have the same things
to tell each other. But ladies first.

472
00:47:26,733 --> 00:47:30,728
But it's going to take time to finish.
- I'll take a nap then.

473
00:47:30,730 --> 00:47:34,099
I can sleep later.
- This is so interesting...

474
00:47:34,101 --> 00:47:37,222
that you'll have a tough time
believing it.

475
00:47:37,222 --> 00:47:40,677
It happened when we performed
in Simla two months ago.

476
00:47:44,215 --> 00:47:48,045
After the show we danced
"and enjoyed so much, you know."

477
00:47:48,793 --> 00:47:53,873
And then I slept so much that
I woke up to find everyone gone.

478
00:47:54,373 --> 00:47:56,579
Those in the van thought I was on
the bus and those on the bus...

479
00:47:56,579 --> 00:47:59,324
thought I was in the van. And in
the confusion I'd been left behind.

480
00:47:59,326 --> 00:48:03,697
That very day we were to perform
at Manali. I didn't know what to do.

481
00:48:04,280 --> 00:48:07,693
"Just then, I saw a helicopter"
land on the hotel lawn.

482
00:48:16,891 --> 00:48:19,846
Whose chopper is this?
- Mr. Karan Singhaniya's.

483
00:48:19,847 --> 00:48:25,510
Why?
"- Oh I was just curious, thank you."

484
00:48:27,132 --> 00:48:31,751
I'm Kajal. I am a friend
"of your boss, Mr. Karan Singhaniya."

485
00:48:40,034 --> 00:48:42,864
Karan and I were supposed to go to
Manali together. I am doing a show.

486
00:48:42,864 --> 00:48:45,945
And he's the chief guest.
You must be aware of all this.

487
00:48:45,945 --> 00:48:49,318
"Yes, I am."
- So will you be here long?

488
00:48:49,817 --> 00:48:53,106
"No, I am on my way to Delhi."
- Since Manali is on the way.

489
00:48:53,523 --> 00:48:56,934
Do you mind dropping me there?
"- No, I can't do that."

490
00:48:56,934 --> 00:48:59,847
"If my boss gets to hear of it,"
I could lose my job.

491
00:48:59,847 --> 00:49:02,927
"What rubbish! Don't worry about that,"
I can explain things to Karan.

492
00:49:02,929 --> 00:49:05,882
But Miss Kajal...
- You ought to be delighted.

493
00:49:05,884 --> 00:49:09,588
"I will talk to Karan about you, and"
it can even fetch you a promotion.

494
00:49:09,588 --> 00:49:12,293
All right.

495
00:49:12,295 --> 00:49:14,623
Don't run away.

496
00:49:14,625 --> 00:49:18,288
I won't.

497
00:49:18,289 --> 00:49:23,076
My bluff worked. I was on my way
to Manali on the helicopter.

498
00:49:23,574 --> 00:49:26,820
But what did I see on the way?
The pilot was stealing glances at me.

499
00:49:27,322 --> 00:49:30,900
"Soon, I could stand it no longer."
I snapped at him.

500
00:49:30,900 --> 00:49:36,353
Haven't you seen a girl before?

501
00:49:36,355 --> 00:49:38,226
What happened after that?
- As soon as I reached Manali...

502
00:49:38,228 --> 00:49:40,056
I slapped that Kamal.
- Kamal? Who?

503
00:49:40,059 --> 00:49:42,887
The same guy you beat up during
the rehearsal of the play.

504
00:49:42,889 --> 00:49:47,800
But the best part was something else.
Guess who was the chief guest?

505
00:49:48,175 --> 00:49:50,340
Who was it?
- Karan Singhaniya.

506
00:49:50,340 --> 00:49:53,503
The owner of the helicopter?
- The owner was himself the pilot.

507
00:49:54,003 --> 00:49:56,581
What are you saying?
"- Raj, I got such a shock..."

508
00:49:56,583 --> 00:50:00,246
when the organizers invited him
on stage. There he was before me!

509
00:50:00,246 --> 00:50:02,576
Miss Kajal.
She directed this play.

510
00:50:02,577 --> 00:50:06,072
"And this is our chief guest,"
Mr. Karan Singhaniya.

511
00:50:06,074 --> 00:50:09,862
I hope you will talk
to my boss Mr. Eeshwar Singhaniya.

512
00:50:12,733 --> 00:50:14,898
You were having fun at my expense.
Couldn't you tell me...

513
00:50:14,898 --> 00:50:17,271
you were Karan Singhaniya?
- You never gave me an opportunity.

514
00:50:17,271 --> 00:50:21,806
What do you mean? Did I stick
a tape round your mouth?

515
00:50:21,806 --> 00:50:25,472
"I thought you were doing me a favour,"
when you were pulling my leg.

516
00:50:26,054 --> 00:50:30,047
"No, I wasn't. On the contrary..."

517
00:50:30,050 --> 00:50:33,380
I'm sorry I lied to you the other day.
"- No, you didn't lie."

518
00:50:33,380 --> 00:50:39,628
"The fact is, you have become"
Karan Singhaniya's friend.

519
00:50:42,371 --> 00:50:46,867
May I ask you a favour?
Can I drop you back at Simla?

520
00:50:47,699 --> 00:50:52,485
"No, I am not going back to Simla."
"I'm headed home, Dehradun."

521
00:50:53,693 --> 00:50:57,771
It's on the way.

522
00:50:57,771 --> 00:51:01,018
Karan dropped me right here.
When the copter landed...

523
00:51:01,018 --> 00:51:05,014
all the boys came running to
"greet us. Manjit, Anurag, Raman..."

524
00:51:05,014 --> 00:51:07,096
everyone was stunned.

525
00:51:07,097 --> 00:51:09,344
"When I thanked Karan, he said,"
Won't you at least...

526
00:51:09,344 --> 00:51:12,007
offer me a cup of coffee
for dropping you here?

527
00:51:12,007 --> 00:51:14,713
I borrowed Manjit's cycle
to take him home.

528
00:51:14,713 --> 00:51:17,918
You seem to be the boss around here.
- They're all my friends.

529
00:51:18,458 --> 00:51:20,998
Is there a special friend among them?
"- I do, but he's away..."

530
00:51:21,000 --> 00:51:24,079
undergoing training with the air force.
His name is Raj.

531
00:51:24,079 --> 00:51:29,780
He is my best friend. We've been
friends since childhood.

532
00:51:29,782 --> 00:51:32,820
He's very fond of me.
He could die for me.

533
00:51:32,820 --> 00:51:36,150
"When we reached home, my parents"
were so surprised at seeing Karan.

534
00:51:36,150 --> 00:51:43,186
But he won over everybody's heart.
He touched the elders' feet...

535
00:51:44,018 --> 00:51:47,347
even GI Joe's.

536
00:51:47,347 --> 00:51:49,552
Embrace me.

537
00:51:49,552 --> 00:51:52,757
He suggested some ayurvedic remedies
for grandma's pain in the knees.

538
00:51:52,759 --> 00:51:56,295
Gave father some Italian recipes
for his canteen.

539
00:51:56,297 --> 00:51:59,043
He even helped mummy
fry some pakoras.

540
00:51:59,045 --> 00:52:01,831
"Here, sir."
"- Wow son, in so many years..."

541
00:52:01,833 --> 00:52:04,496
we didn't realize we could use
the leaves from own backyard...

542
00:52:04,496 --> 00:52:06,827
to make pakoras.
"- No, it's pathodas."

543
00:52:06,827 --> 00:52:09,449
"Yes, pakoras."
"- No aunt, it's pathodas."

544
00:52:09,449 --> 00:52:15,072
You know it's made of leaves.
(Patta - Leaf)

545
00:52:19,273 --> 00:52:22,103
"On Karan's invitation,"
Papa visited his house once.

546
00:52:22,105 --> 00:52:24,434
He couldn't stop talking about them
when he returned. He said...

547
00:52:24,434 --> 00:52:28,097
"They are so rich,"
and yet so humble.

548
00:52:28,099 --> 00:52:31,385
"Then, one day, Karan took me"
to the flying club.

549
00:52:31,929 --> 00:52:37,047
"Where, all his choppers"
were lined up.

550
00:52:37,047 --> 00:52:42,333
"Tell me, which chopper"
would you like to sit in?

551
00:52:42,333 --> 00:52:47,163
What do you call that red one?
- Cessna 172.

552
00:52:48,494 --> 00:52:54,242
That's the one.
"- Hop right in, then."

553
00:52:56,070 --> 00:53:01,190
In that big chopper he flew me across
the clouds. What a sight it was!

554
00:53:02,065 --> 00:53:05,186
"Really Raj, I had never seen"
such clouds before. Then he said...

555
00:53:12,014 --> 00:53:16,590
What did you tell him?

556
00:53:16,592 --> 00:53:19,920
What could I say?
My heart was pounding.

557
00:53:19,922 --> 00:53:23,126
I missed you so much that moment.
I thought...

558
00:53:23,126 --> 00:53:26,539
"if only you had been there,"
I'd have asked you for an answer.

559
00:53:26,539 --> 00:53:30,119
I told Karan just that.
- What did you say?

560
00:53:30,119 --> 00:53:34,197
That I can't say yes or no
without consulting Raj.

561
00:53:34,199 --> 00:53:39,610
"If I forbid you from marrying him,"
you won't marry Karan?

562
00:53:40,152 --> 00:53:43,563
I won't. Promise.
But at least meet him once.

563
00:53:43,565 --> 00:53:46,978
He is so nice that
"you won't forbid me, believe me."

564
00:53:46,978 --> 00:53:49,556
Now that I have told you about
"my wedding, you tell me..."

565
00:53:49,559 --> 00:53:52,887
what did you want to tell me?
"- About your wedding, of course."

566
00:53:52,889 --> 00:53:58,594
When can I meet him?
- You mean it?

567
00:53:59,965 --> 00:54:06,378
Then we'll meet him right away.
Let's go. Come on.

568
00:54:18,862 --> 00:54:24,195
What happened?
- I'll go and freshen up.

569
00:54:35,387 --> 00:54:38,717
Kajal talks a lot about you.
She's very fond of you.

570
00:54:39,384 --> 00:54:42,088
She respects you a lot.
"- Yes, I know."

571
00:54:42,090 --> 00:54:45,293
"My life is in your hands now, sir."
Only you can help me.

572
00:54:45,710 --> 00:54:49,414
"I'm a nice guy, and I come from"
a very good family. I promise you...

573
00:54:49,414 --> 00:54:52,577
I will not let Kajal down. Never.

574
00:54:52,579 --> 00:54:55,951
My folks and I will always
take good care of Kajal.

575
00:54:58,364 --> 00:55:01,735
"Honestly, I dearly love Kajal, sir."

576
00:55:01,737 --> 00:55:05,315
She loves me too.
"As for me, I can't live without her."

577
00:55:07,023 --> 00:55:10,101
"If I don't have Kajal,"
I will die.

578
00:55:10,103 --> 00:55:14,724
"So please put in a kind word for me,"
or Kajal will not marry me.

579
00:55:17,096 --> 00:55:19,760
It's you Karan!

580
00:55:19,760 --> 00:55:23,422
I hope you aren't bribing Raj?
- He doesn't need to.

581
00:55:23,422 --> 00:55:26,418
You can't get a better
life-partner than Karan.

582
00:55:26,420 --> 00:55:32,251
"Oh sir, thank you so much."

583
00:56:52,501 --> 00:56:55,496
If you love someone...

584
00:56:55,498 --> 00:56:58,159
say it...

585
00:56:58,161 --> 00:57:04,030
before it's too late

586
00:57:04,030 --> 00:57:06,943
If you trust someone...

587
00:57:06,945 --> 00:57:09,731
say it...

588
00:57:09,733 --> 00:57:15,938
before it's too late

589
00:57:16,601 --> 00:57:20,847
That's the secret to steal a heart

590
00:58:14,376 --> 00:58:16,581
The pain love inflicts...

591
00:58:16,583 --> 00:58:20,244
"the more it hurts,"
the more you seek

592
00:58:20,246 --> 00:58:24,532
But it's beyond one's comprehension

593
00:58:25,907 --> 00:58:28,612
My beloved...

594
00:58:28,612 --> 00:58:31,608
is a trifle merciless

595
00:58:31,610 --> 00:58:35,938
She takes pleasure in tormenting me

596
00:58:37,271 --> 00:58:41,931
"Yet, my heart is proud"
of my beloved

597
00:58:44,637 --> 00:58:47,634
If you love someone...

598
00:58:47,635 --> 00:58:50,630
express it...

599
00:58:50,632 --> 00:58:57,045
before it's too late

600
00:59:20,686 --> 00:59:23,681
It's a time to celebrate

601
00:59:23,681 --> 00:59:26,679
"A joyous occasion, indeed"

602
00:59:26,679 --> 00:59:30,967
It's the sign
of joyous events to come

603
00:59:32,047 --> 00:59:34,838
It shows in the eyes

604
00:59:34,838 --> 00:59:38,001
That's the wonder of love

605
00:59:38,001 --> 00:59:41,956
Love can never be hidden

606
00:59:43,413 --> 00:59:47,992
Love is a secret
that only the eyes reveal

607
00:59:51,030 --> 00:59:53,693
If you love someone...

608
00:59:53,695 --> 00:59:56,690
express it...

609
00:59:56,692 --> 01:00:02,643
before it's too late

610
01:00:02,643 --> 01:00:05,099
If you trust someone...

611
01:00:05,099 --> 01:00:08,221
say it...

612
01:00:08,222 --> 01:00:14,552
before it's too late

613
01:00:15,005 --> 01:00:20,043
That's the secret to steal a heart

614
01:01:04,414 --> 01:01:08,159
"Bhabhi, why did Raj quit the party?"

615
01:01:08,161 --> 01:01:10,907
Why don't you answer me?
"Tell me, for my sake please."

616
01:01:10,909 --> 01:01:14,697
What do I say?
Raj madly loves you.

617
01:01:15,195 --> 01:01:20,818
He wanted to marry you.

618
01:01:49,827 --> 01:01:55,659
"Tears of joy, you know."
I'm so happy that...

619
01:01:57,320 --> 01:02:00,483
Why didn't you tell me before?

620
01:02:00,483 --> 01:02:03,771
Tell what?
- That you love me.

621
01:02:07,309 --> 01:02:11,054
I never felt the need to tell you.

622
01:02:11,056 --> 01:02:16,009
I thought it was plain enough
for you to see.

623
01:02:16,010 --> 01:02:19,838
It is rightly said that...

624
01:02:19,840 --> 01:02:25,750
a book that is too close to your eyes
cannot be read.

625
01:02:27,331 --> 01:02:32,746
I'm so stupid.

626
01:02:34,199 --> 01:02:38,777
Would you tell me something?
- What?

627
01:02:41,150 --> 01:02:47,186
"Had I proposed you first,"
would your reply have been yes?

628
01:02:49,476 --> 01:02:56,177
Why do you ask me now Raj?
- I won't be at peace till I know.

629
01:02:58,092 --> 01:03:00,880
Neither will you after you know.

630
01:03:00,882 --> 01:03:05,793
"The truth is, I myself don't know."
I never thought about it before.

631
01:03:07,251 --> 01:03:11,911
And it'd be a sin to think of it now.

632
01:03:11,911 --> 01:03:16,905
But don't think that
I'd be spared once I'm away.

633
01:03:16,907 --> 01:03:21,237
"If you hurt yourself, I'll be"
"hurt, too. Remember this much."

634
01:03:32,016 --> 01:03:36,387
The world does not come to an end
if a loved one leaves you.

635
01:03:36,387 --> 01:03:41,257
And if that makes for an excuse
to ruin your own life...

636
01:03:42,547 --> 01:03:47,460
that'd be an insult to your love
and to the one who has left you.

637
01:03:48,916 --> 01:03:53,869
I'm sure you won't ever insult me.
Take care of yourself.

638
01:03:54,911 --> 01:04:00,367
Get a hold on yourself.

639
01:04:34,079 --> 01:04:36,992
There's joy in my eyes...

640
01:04:36,994 --> 01:04:39,989
yet my heart weeps

641
01:04:39,989 --> 01:04:44,320
"Oh, what crossroads"
has love brought me to?

642
01:04:45,318 --> 01:04:50,273
"Yes, it's a secret to endure pain"

643
01:05:43,969 --> 01:05:49,800
"Raj, your brother and bhabhi"
are here.

644
01:05:54,416 --> 01:05:57,536
Fine brother. What brings you here?
- We're on our way back from a seminar

645
01:05:57,538 --> 01:06:01,034
We thought we'd drop in.
"Tell me something, officer..."

646
01:06:01,034 --> 01:06:04,197
have you sworn not to come home?
"- Not at all, brother."

647
01:06:04,199 --> 01:06:07,110
There is so much work here...
- Cut the crap.

648
01:06:07,112 --> 01:06:11,023
You will come home
during the next vacation.

649
01:06:11,025 --> 01:06:15,231
We don't like it without you there.

650
01:06:16,018 --> 01:06:19,181
"Kiran, where are the sweets?"

651
01:06:19,184 --> 01:06:21,139
In the car.
- I'll get them.

652
01:06:21,139 --> 01:06:26,467
Left my favorite stuff in the car?
"- Take him to task, Kiran."

653
01:06:26,469 --> 01:06:30,380
"Take a seat, bhabhi."

654
01:06:30,380 --> 01:06:35,001
"You know Raj, why your brother got"
himself transferred to Nainital?

655
01:06:36,041 --> 01:06:38,536
So that you don't have to travel
all the way to Dehradun.

656
01:06:38,538 --> 01:06:42,034
"I know, bhabhi."

657
01:06:42,036 --> 01:06:46,364
He doesn't want you to be reminded
of the past and hurt yourself.

658
01:06:48,362 --> 01:06:55,980
Yet you make him sad. You neither
come home nor reply to my letters.

659
01:06:56,271 --> 01:06:59,393
"Bhabhi, all you do in the letters"
is ask me to marry.

660
01:06:59,601 --> 01:07:04,849
I don't want to marry.

661
01:07:10,090 --> 01:07:16,001
"All right, I will do just as you say,"
but please stop weeping.

662
01:07:16,251 --> 01:07:19,746
Wipe your tears.
My friends are watching.

663
01:07:19,748 --> 01:07:23,077
"You won't change your mind,"
"will you, Raj?"

664
01:07:23,077 --> 01:07:25,117
No more turning back in life.

665
01:07:25,117 --> 01:07:29,445
"Here are the sweets. Tell me, have"
you fixed the date for coming home?

666
01:07:30,112 --> 01:07:34,481
I'll be in Europe for 6 to 8 weeks
"on a Sea-Harrier training, brother."

667
01:07:35,440 --> 01:07:40,521
"As soon as I return,"
I'll come home.

668
01:08:31,509 --> 01:08:33,631
No good being in a foreign land
all these days.

669
01:08:33,631 --> 01:08:35,671
What do you mean?
- We haven't gone sightseeing.

670
01:08:35,671 --> 01:08:38,707
"I mean, no women and wine..."
"- He's right. Come on, let's go."

671
01:08:38,710 --> 01:08:42,456
It's New Year's Eve. Must celebrate.
"- All right, let's go to the disco."

672
01:08:42,706 --> 01:08:46,203
"Wow, that's a great idea."
- Even the toughest one has ideas!

673
01:08:46,203 --> 01:08:50,114
Busted! His little secret
has been discovered.

674
01:09:17,212 --> 01:09:23,042
"Monty, let go. What are you doing?"

675
01:09:30,742 --> 01:09:33,694
"Same for him, please."
What are you staring at?

676
01:09:33,697 --> 01:09:36,194
Haven't you seen a girl booze?

677
01:09:36,194 --> 01:09:40,149
"Actually, I don't usually drink."
But today is New Year's Eve.

678
01:09:40,398 --> 01:09:43,520
So I thought I'd live it up.
I'd try something new.

679
01:09:48,265 --> 01:09:53,096
"You see, tonight..."

680
01:09:55,259 --> 01:10:00,587
"I'm slightly drunk. When I drink,"
it hits me very fast.

681
01:10:00,752 --> 01:10:04,247
Aren't you stoned?

682
01:10:04,250 --> 01:10:08,411
A torn pocket!

683
01:10:08,412 --> 01:10:11,576
I suppose you don't know this
is in fashion these days.

684
01:10:12,948 --> 01:10:16,569
It's an Armani jacket.
- It's now a typical Sindhi jacket!

685
01:10:17,444 --> 01:10:20,608
"Listen, please give me your residence"
"number, telephone number, everything."

686
01:10:21,814 --> 01:10:25,645
"Mr. Never Mind, give me your address."
I will send you a jacket.

687
01:10:26,310 --> 01:10:29,430
